2:T72f,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Murf AI better than Otter.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Murf AI scores 7.0 overall while Otter.ai scores 8.0. Murf AI is best for corporate presentations and e-learning voiceovers, while Otter.ai excels for meeting transcription and journalists and students."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Murf AI or Otter.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Murf AI starts at $23/mo and Otter.ai starts at $8.33/mo. Murf AI offers a free plan. Otter.ai offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Murf AI to Otter.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Murf AI and Otter.ai support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Murf AI vs Otter.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Murf AI holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Otter.ai has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise Murf AI for professional voice quality and Otter.ai for excellent real-time transcription."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Murf AI or Otter.ai?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Otter.ai for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Murf AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize professional voice quality. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html