7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Murf AI and Otter.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Api Access. Where Murf AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Text To Speech and Voice Cloning and Multilingual and Custom Voices, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Otter.ai uniquely offers Speech To Text and Real Time, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Murf AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Otter.ai scores 8/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Otter.ai comes in at a lower starting price of $8.33/mo, while Murf AI begins at $23/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Murf AI's free tier and Otter.ai's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
